snippet.title: Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 14 (PS2) - Intro
snippet.description:
The intro cinematic for Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu 14, a 2007 baseball video game by Konami. Reuploading in higher quality.

The theme song is Shining Road by MAKI.
